--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- This file is to create tutorial events.
-- Tutorial events are 100% trigger chance events that serve to explain a little bit of what's going on behind the scenes and perhaps give a little warning. (e.g. "Just a tip! Building cities away from water makes them vulnerable to fire.")
-- Tutorial events should be under 'EVENT_CLASS_TRADE' so they can be turned off by the Player.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

